    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0396c03"/><ptr target="fn22"/><lb ed="T" n="0396c03"/><persName key="A002300">釋賢護</persName>，姓孫，<placeName key="PL000000045052">涼州</placeName>人。來止<placeName key="PL000000035339">廣漢閻興寺</placeName>，常<lb ed="T" n="0396c05"/>習禪定為業，又善於律行，纖毫無犯。以<lb ed="T" n="0396c06"/><date key="j18675531867936" from-iso="0401-01-31" to-iso="0402-02-18">晉隆安五年</date>卒，臨亡口出五色光明，照滿<lb ed="T" n="0396c07"/><placeName key="PL000000035339">寺</placeName>內。遺言使燒身，弟子行之，既而<ptr target="fn23"/>支節都<lb ed="T" n="0396c08"/>盡，<ptr target="fn24"/>唯一指不然，<ptr target="fn25"/>因埋之塔下。</p>
